### 公开接口：获取所有激活的研究学科列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/research-subjects
Accept: application/json

### 公开接口：根据ID获取特定激活的研究学科
GET http://localhost:8080/api/research-subjects/{{researchSubjectId}}
Accept: application/json

### 平台管理员获取所有研究学科列表（包括未激活的）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/manage/research-subjects
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_platform_admin}}
Accept: application/json

### 平台管理员根据ID获取特定研究学科（无论是否激活）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/manage/research-subjects/{{researchSubjectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_platform_admin}}
Accept: application/json

### 平台管理员创建新的研究学科
POST http://localhost:8080/api/manage/research-subjects
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_platform_admin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "临床医学",
  "nameEn": "Clinical Medicine",
  "description": "研究疾病的病因、诊断、治疗和预后等的医学学科",
  "active": false
}

### 平台管理员更新研究学科
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/manage/research-subjects/{{researchSubjectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_platform_admin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "基础医学",
  "nameEn": "Basic Medicine",
  "description": "研究人体生命活动规律的基础学科",
  "active": false
}

### 平台管理员删除研究学科
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/manage/research-subjects/{{researchSubjectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_platform_admin}}